                                <p class="summary" style="white-space: pre-line">Genetic Savings &amp; Clone was a genetic services company that offered commercial pet gene banking and cloning. Mr. Robison was responsible for architecting, developing and deploying Clonesoft, custom business process automation software that ran every aspect of the business from the website to cloned pet delivery.</p>
                                    <ul>
                                            <li>Cloned a cat and delivered it to customer.</li>
