                                <p class="summary" style="white-space: pre-line">As Technical Director for Interactivate, Inc., Mr. Robison&#x27;s responsibilities were extensive and included, but were not limited to managing and maintaining IT resources including customer applications and websites.  Help grow the company from 10 to 65 employees. .</p>
